<figureCitation id="8AD037FC516E0D91FDC038EF486AEFE6" captionStart="Figures 4–9" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figures 4 - 9. Aulacus flavus. 4 Lateral (scale bar = 1.0 mm) 5 Head, lateral 6 Head, dorsal 7 Head, front 8 Mesosoma dorsal 9 Mesosoma, lateral." figureDoi="10.3897/jhr.53.9902.figures4-9" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/115577" pageId="2" pageNumber="165">Figs 4-9</figureCitation>
